	 ('c819ea0d-8fb9-4aab-a4c7-2d2c1c67eac5'::uuid,'GIBBS-SMITH','PERSON','{}','GIBBS-SMITH is a historian renowned for compiling and documenting the critical figures and chronological milestones in the early advancements of powered flight. Their extensive research provides valuable insights into the pioneers and events that shaped this significant period in aviation history, offering a comprehensive timeline of developments from the inception to the early stages of powered flight technology.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["61646302e3bc960c352c6408cdc69191dab988abf38ec4bf7f2e4174aba91d86396e3e37ae38ca304afb1a34043af419361016661c11be52244507e7a8027a39", "61646302e3bc960c352c6408cdc69191dab988abf38ec4bf7f2e4174aba91d86396e3e37ae38ca304afb1a34043af419361016661c11be52244507e7a8027a39"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('95a759cf-aa56-4bf9-b0ae-15884c62c8a3'::uuid,'LUNDBERG WHIRLING ARM DEVICE','MECHANISM','{}','Cayley''s whirling arm device was used to conduct experiments on aerofoil properties like lift and drag, leading to the discovery of better lift from cambered surfaces. It also helped in understanding centre of pressure positioning.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 1, "text_unit_ids": ["f5cd08a5bba8e5f1cac73b2168b03f440d049e82b880cf5ff9b03a61f932ab149f55ecbff1e2e45fc298cd176b96304c704c6f0d04ce87977c3be47e617c941b"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics');

After the conclusion of World War I, there was a notable shift in the use and collaboration between these wind tunnel research centers. Germany and its influential contributions, especially through the work of Ludwig Prandtl and his pioneering tunnels, played a critical role. The post-WWI period witnessed an increasing reliance on German equipment by researchers from France, Britain, Italy, and America. Notably, figures like Max Munk contributed to this transfer of knowledge and technology, moving abroad to continue research in other countries that adopted the German methodologies.

This transition facilitated a cross-pollination of ideas and practical ap','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["75e55aae79fa4fef8afa00e4bf79f6f1f694d27b10f227c1f393bd8cf61700080ce3c057271ae7311d2d3cd09b4445ff1281543e67c2ce7840a138c9f1467077", "75e55aae79fa4fef8afa00e4bf79f6f1f694d27b10f227c1f393bd8cf61700080ce3c057271ae7311d2d3cd09b4445ff1281543e67c2ce7840a138c9f1467077"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('7426ecfe-36c1-4f6c-aeb8-7bf6f302fe28'::uuid,'ROTATIONAL VELOCITY REGULATION','MECHANISM','{}','Mechanism responsible for controlling the speed of whirling arms, poor until electric motors came into use>','{}','{}','{"frequency": 3, "text_unit_ids": ["bad2d51ceb36600b316dd9e9559a9c537449b7988c1b3cff40a6201ad6c19b9adb9b92e7900d7b444e642f5b22112ecf93bb086b0a57f7bc5ec5e294e014471a", "bad2d51ceb36600b316dd9e9559a9c537449b7988c1b3cff40a6201ad6c19b9adb9b92e7900d7b444e642f5b22112ecf93bb086b0a57f7bc5ec5e294e014471a", "bad2d51ceb36600b316dd9e9559a9c537449b7988c1b3cff40a6201ad6c19b9adb9b92e7900d7b444e642f5b22112ecf93bb086b0a57f7bc5ec5e294e014471a"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('15203f47-2b8b-4b5f-9b85-a705584564e4'::uuid,'FINITE WING PERFORMANCE MEASUREMENT','TEST','{}','Using whirling arms to measure the drag and lift on wing sections, both finite and propeller, contributing knowledge to aircraft design>','{}','{}','{"frequency": 3, "text_unit_ids": ["bad2d51ceb36600b316dd9e9559a9c537449b7988c1b3cff40a6201ad6c19b9adb9b92e7900d7b444e642f5b22112ecf93bb086b0a57f7bc5ec5e294e014471a", "bad2d51ceb36600b316dd9e9559a9c537449b7988c1b3cff40a6201ad6c19b9adb9b92e7900d7b444e642f5b22112ecf93bb086b0a57f7bc5ec5e294e014471a", "bad2d51ceb36600b316dd9e9559a9c537449b7988c1b3cff40a6201ad6c19b9adb9b92e7900d7b444e642f5b22112ecf93bb086b0a57f7bc5ec5e294e014471a"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('e40e8cf4-eb89-41c5-9b77-e553261e529c'::uuid,'AEROFOILS WITH THE BEST PERFORMANCE','MODEL','{}','The shape of early model aerofoils varied depending on Reynolds number; thin aerofoils were used at lower Reynolds numbers due to structural limitations','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["61646302e3bc960c352c6408cdc69191dab988abf38ec4bf7f2e4174aba91d86396e3e37ae38ca304afb1a34043af419361016661c11be52244507e7a8027a39", "61646302e3bc960c352c6408cdc69191dab988abf38ec4bf7f2e4174aba91d86396e3e37ae38ca304afb1a34043af419361016661c11be52244507e7a8027a39"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics');

Da Vinci also played a crucial role in the conceptualization of human flight, an area where his innovative ideas were ahead of their time. He conceived multiple projects and drafted detailed sketches intended to facilitate human flight, even though he did not see these designs through into practical implementations. It was only later centuries that engineers and scientists would build on his theoretical work to bring some of these concepts to fruition. Thus, while da Vinci may not have ','{}','{}','{"frequency": 3, "text_unit_ids": ["29d7b9fb394697229d5c6ee7e8e7498c26b62969f8ef9bf5c71dde024c555e26c654c119dc856911c2890b719150da3d3016b67a8e15863bf865abc974c1efb6", "29d7b9fb394697229d5c6ee7e8e7498c26b62969f8ef9bf5c71dde024c555e26c654c119dc856911c2890b719150da3d3016b67a8e15863bf865abc974c1efb6", "2e9ab909fa00e8633f612e2ff91a1104e10bcb90497c34e3402b71ef3457891e98b8a02caae3e6e229aac92c0c890dbd32b2f49dd7eb38da47a97c5e1a2a24ca"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics');

Unfortunately, Pilcher faced one such challenge himself. While attempting a hang gliding flight under difficult weather conditions, he lost control and was fatally injured in an accident. This tragic event highlights the inherent risks associated with being among the first to explore and push the boundaries of human flight through lighter-than-air technologies. Despite his untimely death, Pilcher''s contributions to early aviation—especially his collaborative efforts with Lilienthal—have left a lasting l','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["71513cc51ffa1e8b185f20e95d505c81a39cad56f6db7e0192988badc6a212324cd2dca2a6e0b895668f6133ccf33ae88b3164f544f6ed7f319db021e5f84305", "f5cd08a5bba8e5f1cac73b2168b03f440d049e82b880cf5ff9b03a61f932ab149f55ecbff1e2e45fc298cd176b96304c704c6f0d04ce87977c3be47e617c941b"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('d2b80229-2cb6-4dfd-aeba-4c29e057bd7f'::uuid,'CHANUTE','PERSON','{}','William Joseph "Billy" Chanute made significant contributions to the field of aerodynamics through his support for pioneering aviators. While Chanute himself did not serve as an aviator, he actively contributed to early aviation research by providing financial backing and encouragement to notable figures such as Otto Lilienthal, who was a leading figure in glider research during the late 19th century. Additionally, Chanute''s support extended beyond Lilienthal; he also collaborated with other prominent individuals involved in aviation research at the turn of the century. Notably, records indicate his work overlapped with that of the Wright brothers, aligning with their efforts to advance aerodynamic principles and aircraft design. Through his dedicated financial assistance and intellectual engagement, Chanute played a crucial role in fostering an environment conducive to the development of aviation technology, thereby making him a pivotal figure in early 20th-century aeronautical resear','{}','{}','{"frequency": 3, "text_unit_ids": ["71513cc51ffa1e8b185f20e95d505c81a39cad56f6db7e0192988badc6a212324cd2dca2a6e0b895668f6133ccf33ae88b3164f544f6ed7f319db021e5f84305", "5b2cda8d5bbd5d82e2c6fdbd3f95d22ccf5c61786e126e8b0c5e7391999cff6606a62534e3cc3ff179c861f6e0cb19ee489f79b583fb0cfba038d14349b9403b", "5b2cda8d5bbd5d82e2c6fdbd3f95d22ccf5c61786e126e8b0c5e7391999cff6606a62534e3cc3ff179c861f6e0cb19ee489f79b583fb0cfba038d14349b9403b"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('0ff30a45-c20f-4829-b1bc-fb3fc79e3ff7'::uuid,'WING_TAPER','MECHANISM','{}','A design characteristic that varies the width or thickness of a wing along its length, crucial for optimizing aerodynamic performance but poorly understood at the time.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 1, "text_unit_ids": ["71513cc51ffa1e8b185f20e95d505c81a39cad56f6db7e0192988badc6a212324cd2dca2a6e0b895668f6133ccf33ae88b3164f544f6ed7f319db021e5f84305"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('2a6b03ed-545d-4374-b293-8a825fe55185'::uuid,'WEISBACH LAMINAR COEFFICIENT','MODEL','{}','The WEISBACH LAMINAR COEFFICIENT is a key model used to predict and understand the behavior of fluid flow. This coefficient is particularly important as it aids in comprehending viscous forces within fluids, which are essential for calculating drag forces. The model''s utility extends through its connection with Reynolds numbers, highlighting its significance in analyzing both laminar and transitional flows where such forces play a critical role. By incorporating this coefficient, engineers and scientists can more accurately assess fluid dynamics scenarios, ensuring applications from mechanical engineering to environmental science benefit from meticulous flow predictions.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["da2c68ea72d6096891cf006fbb7859eb6086b57f5f126736a57dd65bf1b0e2133cdc19753df3049b79ab1e71a91e46e9d3764b949686b623843529cf5f38774b", "da2c68ea72d6096891cf006fbb7859eb6086b57f5f126736a57dd65bf1b0e2133cdc19753df3049b79ab1e71a91e46e9d3764b949686b623843529cf5f38774b"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('7c3082e0-864c-43ae-a2c3-4318f96962dd'::uuid,'WHIRLING ARMS','DEVICE','{}','"Whirling Arms," a device utilized in both fluid mechanics and aerodynamics studies, consists of a spinning arm equipped with a model. This apparatus serves multiple critical functions in experimental setups. Primarily, whirling arms are essential tools for calibrating hot wire anemometry to ensure accurate measurements of velocity fields within the spinning model''s wake. Additionally, they play a vital role in investigating dynamic models and measuring stability derivatives, providing valuable data on aerodynamic performance under various conditions. The comprehensive nature of these devices makes them indispensable for researchers and engineers seeking detailed insights into fluid dynamics and aerodynamic behaviors through controlled experiments.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 3, "text_unit_ids": ["98f5af20b50979a6ceae00e0e262a4696f43fcd93e841c5eef7dcf55961a4513c7b0217df7f06d0572fe3bf238235fca6779737f60a3dedb4741275610b14f03", "98f5af20b50979a6ceae00e0e262a4696f43fcd93e841c5eef7dcf55961a4513c7b0217df7f06d0572fe3bf238235fca6779737f60a3dedb4741275610b14f03", "653aa46087e791b134dbbd802cc7f2be070fd13ba9b27acc8585793069a21cb0efa3b5f8653b3d05323cc3ed759a463b78204a2bc4749488e28d38de3050a9cc"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics');

The airship, piloted by Giffard himself, served as a pioneering venture that laid groundwork for future advancements in dirigibles. While it represented a critical juncture in the development of air transportation technology, it also highlighted limitations in early designs, particularly in terms of advanced control mechanisms. Despite these constraints, it remains an essential part of the evolution of flying machines, bridging the gap between theoretical concepts and practical applications in aerial navigation during the mid-19th century.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 3, "text_unit_ids": ["4089000a7a5f43c1f79ebd955ed69dab8fc13c6f0153fe4c6ae9df3fdfa0ecdfc28e259193c210fc04e64e6f124fe76ccb1f7ccbb3e5ccb8e8d848fbdfd2ef5c", "4089000a7a5f43c1f79ebd955ed69dab8fc13c6f0153fe4c6ae9df3fdfa0ecdfc28e259193c210fc04e64e6f124fe76ccb1f7ccbb3e5ccb8e8d848fbdfd2ef5c", "4089000a7a5f43c1f79ebd955ed69dab8fc13c6f0153fe4c6ae9df3fdfa0ecdfc28e259193c210fc04e64e6f124fe76ccb1f7ccbb3e5ccb8e8d848fbdfd2ef5c"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
