	 ('75c36b22-81b1-4081-a9a0-592039aecc52'::uuid,'OTTO LILIENTHAL','PERSON','{}','Otto Lilienthal, a German engineer and aviation pioneer, made significant contributions to early aviation through his systematic experimentation and glider design. Born in 1848, Lilienthal is best known for his extensive work in hang gliding, conducting over 2,500 successful flights between 1891 and 1896 before his tragic death in a crash on August 10, 1896.

Lilienthal’s pioneering experiments began in 1874 when he conducted free-wind tests that validated theoretical models about aerofoil drag, lift, and polar characteristics. His research confirmed that cambered shapes provided better performance compared to flat plates, validating the importance of airfoil design for aircraft. Building on this work and the experiments conducted by Wenham in earlier years, Lilienthal published his findings in 1889 and went on to develop a series of highly innovative gliders.

Beyond experimentation, Lilienthal also focused on glider design, which influenced not only contemporary aviators but later on','{}','{}','{"frequency": 14, "text_unit_ids": ["ee745461b2211d842e88d29f225a86ba7063e293122d56b41cea0528892369a6d28a8de8ecaaba49f767d0dc0952376d919da861f26599624546ddc82d9781c5", "ee745461b2211d842e88d29f225a86ba7063e293122d56b41cea0528892369a6d28a8de8ecaaba49f767d0dc0952376d919da861f26599624546ddc82d9781c5", "573d5db6e587374521f111a47eaa08e2ce573235b08716d91bbe053504fe503530293339ede873a3ac356c3d376fcb97e005ef76112125385fa9e127d8e42fec", "573d5db6e587374521f111a47eaa08e2ce573235b08716d91bbe053504fe503530293339ede873a3ac356c3d376fcb97e005ef76112125385fa9e127d8e42fec", "ffe9725d362af387144062ce80531a3c181c5efe24e8c5ccb730a3fad8dd8623051f30cc871dc61ff2bf656d91294dc1547d0406b008537b49f8a44cfcec0d79", "ffe9725d362af387144062ce80531a3c181c5efe24e8c5ccb730a3fad8dd8623051f30cc871dc61ff2bf656d91294dc1547d0406b008537b49f8a44cfcec0d79", "624b0f2e5156161ffdb09c558f32b39ad0bf347e1dcc51d0cc803eb1592f75125b51005c9a82dfcfa9afb96df74b8311d90272937604af08308a19e41b14f3c5", "624b0f2e5156161ffdb09c558f32b39ad0bf347e1dcc51d0cc803eb1592f75125b51005c9a82dfcfa9afb96df74b8311d90272937604af08308a19e41b14f3c5", "624b0f2e5156161ffdb09c558f32b39ad0bf347e1dcc51d0cc803eb1592f75125b51005c9a82dfcfa9afb96df74b8311d90272937604af08308a19e41b14f3c5", "a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e", "a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e", "ccac1a178375331bc449ac2d2eec635f0983c00e6d254912345c012c0c41f3a9cc65da465cf715f8bc206801bb7f81cd82c005354ce5454c3970c507c2045930", "b93603f69bb902d6bc4a15e32e34bac0942d14f58f5b7fd54e0187ddc73790c3986b6f906396ba733338823b8e99640c1794d84bcc0a8862b2e18fb964601739", "b93603f69bb902d6bc4a15e32e34bac0942d14f58f5b7fd54e0187ddc73790c3986b6f906396ba733338823b8e99640c1794d84bcc0a