In essence, the Viscous Incompressible Gas Model combines elements of both Newtonian flu','{}','{}','{"frequency": 4, "text_unit_ids": ["22c3c2c423ad221ca214710cfa41f27d1e4dc8d6d2a92cf697c6e413557740e0d79914704f6f8c0e7f4ce8f21bf52fe6505883477ed45d7e212012e482c40ef5", "22c3c2c423ad221ca214710cfa41f27d1e4dc8d6d2a92cf697c6e413557740e0d79914704f6f8c0e7f4ce8f21bf52fe6505883477ed45d7e212012e482c40ef5", "7bab4e0b9bf564415098605230a0b8c9801762a344b1305f6767edd6b3d9c9e7d69c62df8d4aa634a80ec96f8417c044943b33570af019c7be0aee94a675a2da", "7bab4e0b9bf564415098605230a0b8c9801762a344b1305f6767edd6b3d9c9e7d69c62df8d4aa634a80ec96f8417c044943b33570af019c7be0aee94a675a2da"]}','2026-07-17 16:18:55.489892','2026-07-17 16:18:55.489892','aerodynamics_v1'),
