	 ('3ff9316e-64c8-4cb2-83a1-3fcc3659761d'::uuid,'INTERNAL ENGINE','DEVICE','{}','An early powered model propulsion system using gunpowder fuel','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573", "faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('83327a11-f811-4921-844f-a38762a8f5d5'::uuid,'EXTERNAL ENGINE','DEVICE','{}','Another form of propulsion used in models driven by gunpowder','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573", "faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('67e5cc35-3492-4b60-86cc-4a2d6657e9d8'::uuid,'FULL-SCALE CRAFT','SYSTEM','{}','A working model that made an unmanned flight in 1849','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573", "faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('8ad06da2-a77d-42f8-8645-8ae929b4a6f2'::uuid,'UNMANNED CRAFT','MODEL','{}','An unmanned craft tested in Brompton near Scarborough, Yorkshire in 1853','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573", "faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('7db47b1b-303b-4612-a2bd-4c82edab3d0b'::uuid,'STEAM-POWERED FLYING MACHINE','SYSTEM','{}','William Henson patented a steam-powered flying machine to transport mail and goods, developed between 1842 and 1867','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573", "faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('4049c208-4a84-4259-8095-0cf38c4c07db'::uuid,'MODEL HELICOPTER','DEVICE','{}','The MODEL HELICOPTER represents an early technological milestone in the realm of aviation theory and application. Developed by a collaborative team including Ponton d''Amécourt, Nadar, and de Lalande, this device was instrumental not only as a practical tool but also served to test theoretical principles pivotal for achieving controlled flight. The development of the MODEL HELICOPTER aligns with its creators'' broader manifesto emphasizing the pursuit of controlled flight, indicating its significance in advancing the understanding and feasibility of human flight. These innovators leveraged their device to explore foundational concepts that would later be crucial in the evolution of aviation technology.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 3, "text_unit_ids": ["faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573", "faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573", "faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('f27955cd-e000-4a59-a245-6ab69031912a'::uuid,'L''ALBATROS ARTIFICIEL','SYSTEM','{}','Le Bris''s glider that achieved its first successful flight in 1868 with horse-drawn traction on a beach','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573", "faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('8b0f7bbf-a923-482e-88a9-09d24a9b630f'::uuid,'UNMANNED GLIDERS','MODEL','{}','Francis Herbert Wenham attempted to build and test unmanned gliders but was unsuccessful in achieving manned flights, emphasizing the importance of wing shape for lift','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573", "faa334cc3a5b50c3cebcf1df46beb7be9ad777690802933a651dec6cbd0da34c9fef6dd95627eca4b6a746fc7c67bc72b217d1c4e60e92895dbfef4b8412f573"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('67d0ccbc-7b4f-49dc-9ea2-2918c68705e1'::uuid,'FRANCIS HERBERT WENHAM','PERSON','{}','Francis Herbert Wenham attempted to build unmanned gliders and concluded that long thin wings would be more effective than bat-like wings due to their longer leading edge','{}','{}','{"frequency": 1, "text_unit_ids": ["a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('aa449033-0a26-462c-a1bd-6cf983ac6540'::uuid,'BIRD-LIKE WING','MECHANISM','{}','The term "BIRD-LIKE WING" refers to a wing design that mirrors key aspects of avian anatomy. This design focuses on the significant contribution of the front parts of the wing in generating lift, drawing inspiration directly from bird physiology. According to the research by Wenham, this characteristic is crucial for optimizing flight capabilities. The wing''s structure is meticulously crafted to mimic natural bird wings, enhancing its efficiency and effectiveness in various aerodynamic environments. This approach ensures that the leading edge of the wing—a critical component—plays a pivotal role in producing lift, mimicking nature’s sophisticated design in aviation engineering.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e", "a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics');
INSERT INTO agi_evolution.knowledge_nodes (id,"name",node_type,properties,description,embedding,parameters,metadata,created_at,updated_at,theme_id) VALUES
	 ('9c9c5562-1ef1-4c77-a694-fc05ce028454'::uuid,'LONG AND THIN WINGS','MECHANISM','{}','Proposed wing design with a longer leading edge relative to weight, believed to be more effective based on Wenham''s research','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e", "a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('9dfd15f0-70f9-4069-83e8-81b5bf8d5583'::uuid,'PARACHTHTE MODEL','DEVICE','{}','Model proposed by Leonardo da Vinci for reducing fall speed. Demonstrated principles of drag and lift.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["a5d4719b2541caf004e1082010054faa38c7ba80d90b5f7e39636fab5592ad3861a1d6acd00ebc78dac62d343df8f5398463149ba9cee12a0171444fbc1a02ad", "a5d4719b2541caf004e1082010054faa38c7ba80d90b5f7e39636fab5592ad3861a1d6acd00ebc78dac62d343df8f5398463149ba9cee12a0171444fbc1a02ad"]}','2026-07-17 16:18:55.489892','2026-07-17 16:18:55.489892','aerodynamics_v1'),
	 ('cdde7266-3278-4d8f-a70d-f986df6aca6c'::uuid,'HUMANITY','ORGANIZATION','{}','The collective term representing the human experience and practical usage of aerodynamic principles throughout history.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 1, "text_unit_ids": ["c39119a42bf54d5f3a6c528527afa0659b9429b38912e2720b5ab4f6ac9e9979a2f0357e21700957de3eeda5bfae120fd0986c0cbb00355505e8e2ddc1e849ac"]}','2026-07-17 16:18:55.489892','2026-07-17 16:18:55.489892','aerodynamics_v1'),
	 ('7a00603d-b4dc-4e9f-986c-c2166b67ae51'::uuid,'CURVED WINGS','MECHANISM','{}','CURVED WINGS are noted for their superior aerodynamic performance, having been validated through rigorous testing. According to research conducted by Robert Wenham, these wings exhibit enhanced lift efficiency, achieving a notable lift-to-drag ratio of approximately 5:1 when tested at an angle of 15 degrees. The design proves particularly effective due to its optimized curvature, which has been confirmed through extensive wind tunnel experiments. This superior lifting ability makes CURVED WINGS a preferred choice in applications requiring high performance and efficiency in aerodynamic settings.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e", "a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('f125efeb-25ed-4113-9d31-d152697f4c34'::uuid,'ENGINEERED DEVICES','SYSTEM','{}','The ENGINEERED DEVICES discussed were specifically designed for purposes related to gliders and wind tunnels. These devices exemplify early practical contributions to the field of aviation research, highlighting significant advancements in understanding aerodynamics and airplane design during an initial phase of exploration and innovation. Through their construction and utilization, these engineered tools facilitated foundational studies essential for the development of more advanced aircraft technologies.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e", "a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('080bb00f-e8e8-4ad3-b9b0-03f6bf148654'::uuid,'HEAVYER-THAN-AIR CRAFT','MECHANISM','{}','Term referring to aircraft which have a greater weight than air during operation, supported by the demonstration of increased lift performance in Wenham''s research','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e", "a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('85de5b62-7c25-43b1-abfb-78207c4b6a7e'::uuid,'GLEIDFLUGEL (HANG GLIDER)','MECHANISM','{}','Wing design pioneered by Lilienthal that evolved into the modern hang glider, emphasizing jump before you fly concept for aerial stability and control','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e", "a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('f070ce9a-2475-4cf1-8aa4-008a5d79d492'::uuid,'JOHN J. MONTGOMERY''S GLIDER','DEVICE','{}','First truly modern glider constructed near San Diego in 1883, capable of controlled flight with the help of a wind tunnel','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e", "a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('7711cada-8394-452b-a775-902721dfdb84'::uuid,'WILHEM KRESS''S HANG GLIDER','MECHANISM','{}','The WILHEM KRESS''S HANG GLIDER is an early aviation device constructed approximately in 1877. This pioneering hang glider served dual purposes: it was primarily designed to explore the fundamental aerodynamic principles governing aircraft, providing crucial insights into the mechanics of flight. Additionally, this innovative device played a significant role in inspiring further developments in hang gliding and early aviation technology, marking an important milestone in the history of manned flight.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e", "a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('3e81aaeb-0380-4373-902b-3a5f3791fdc2'::uuid,'OTTO LILIENTHAL''S RESEARCH','MECHANISM','{}','OTTO LILIENTHAL''S RESEARCH focused extensively on the development of wing design and stability, building upon the earlier experiments conducted by Wenham. This body of work, resulting in a publication in 1889, substantiated and expanded the foundational findings established by Wenham. Lilienthal''s research was pivotal in advancing the field, as it not only refined existing theories but also provided critical insights that laid groundwork for future aviation developments.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e", "a1689fa4557c7bd9828498b6af22e4d56a6e70b706bc03a66df0ec58854f6cb93cfb6e67be14e6cf7954609e79e3b6bd423a0ba59422819f13f132672854041e"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics');
INSERT INTO agi_evolution.knowledge_nodes (id,"name",node_type,properties,description,embedding,parameters,metadata,created_at,updated_at,theme_id) VALUES
	 ('e92272e0-dcdb-468d-bf9a-79ae1496190d'::uuid,'LILIENTHAL''S LAST GLIDER','DEVICE','{}','"Otto Lilienthal''s last hang glider broke apart in the wind, causing his fatal fall."</|','{}','{}','{"frequency": 1, "text_unit_ids": ["ccac1a178375331bc449ac2d2eec635f0983c00e6d254912345c012c0c41f3a9cc65da465cf715f8bc206801bb7f81cd82c005354ce5454c3970c507c2045930"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('dec89157-0bd3-4104-aaa7-96f2f09cf8b2'::uuid,'AVION III','DEVICE','{}','"Clément Ader''s heavier-than-air aircraft, powered by a steam engine, made short flights."<|','{}','{}','{"frequency": 1, "text_unit_ids": ["ccac1a178375331bc449ac2d2eec635f0983c00e6d254912345c012c0c41f3a9cc65da465cf715f8bc206801bb7f81cd82c005354ce5454c3970c507c2045930"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('2808bbcb-5bf8-4f77-9ed5-2ff78d97fabe'::uuid,'LILIENTHAL''S MACHINE','DEVICE','{}','"Otto Lilienthal used his last hang glider to make flights until its failure in the wind, causing his fall."</|','{}','{}','{"frequency": 1, "text_unit_ids": ["ccac1a178375331bc449ac2d2eec635f0983c00e6d254912345c012c0c41f3a9cc65da465cf715f8bc206801bb7f81cd82c005354ce5454c3970c507c2045930"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('b40f53a9-a48c-4bd7-83aa-421675a5d1f6'::uuid,'Крыло','part','{"создавать подъёмную силу"}','Несущая поверхность летательного аппарата',NULL,'{}','{}','2026-07-17 09:59:49.144477','2026-07-17 09:59:49.144477','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('df4b8235-7111-4782-8860-3366815f007a'::uuid,'Двигатель','device','{"создавать тягу","преобразовывать энергию"}','Силовая установка',NULL,'{}','{}','2026-07-17 09:59:49.144477','2026-07-17 09:59:49.144477','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('b43bc703-73b3-4c0a-944c-e651523090b9'::uuid,'Фюзеляж','part','{перевозить,"вмещать груз"}','Основная несущая часть аппарата',NULL,'{}','{}','2026-07-17 09:59:49.144477','2026-07-17 09:59:49.144477','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('c4a58148-3f09-4b6c-9a65-4b9f0e16aec2'::uuid,'A. F. MOZHAISKY','PERSON','{}','"Alexander Mozhaisky built and tested a monoplane with two steam engines but failed due to lack of funds for continued research."<|','{}','{}','{"frequency": 1, "text_unit_ids": ["ccac1a178375331bc449ac2d2eec635f0983c00e6d254912345c012c0c41f3a9cc65da465cf715f8bc206801bb7f81cd82c005354ce5454c3970c507c2045930"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('9d0aae1a-a6a2-46cb-8573-d3359109a4f3'::uuid,'Руль высоты','component','{"управлять полётом"}','Орган управления по тангажу',NULL,'{}','{}','2026-07-17 09:59:49.144477','2026-07-17 09:59:49.144477','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('90e301ea-6f8e-4732-a3f5-bca7ad30ec29'::uuid,'Элерон','component','{"управлять полётом"}','Орган управления по крену',NULL,'{}','{}','2026-07-17 09:59:49.144477','2026-07-17 09:59:49.144477','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('bc3f06aa-9147-44c8-9c6e-8598b2cea7e9'::uuid,'CLÉMENT ADER','MODEL','{}','"Clément Ader successfully launched the Eole, powered by a steam engine, making a short 50-meter flight near Paris in 1890." "<|','{}','{}','{"frequency": 1, "text_unit_ids": ["ccac1a178375331bc449ac2d2eec635f0983c00e6d254912345c012c0c41f3a9cc65da465cf715f8bc206801bb7f81cd82c005354ce5454c3970c507c2045930"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics');
INSERT INTO agi_evolution.knowledge_nodes (id,"name",node_type,properties,description,embedding,parameters,metadata,created_at,updated_at,theme_id) VALUES
	 ('2dd8253f-47d1-4a5b-bee1-4c4ab03a6d41'::uuid,'EOLE','DEVICE','{}','"The Eole is Clément Ader''s successful first heavier-than-air aircraft tested near Paris.<|""','{}','{}','{"frequency": 1, "text_unit_ids": ["ccac1a178375331bc449ac2d2eec635f0983c00e6d254912345c012c0c41f3a9cc65da465cf715f8bc206801bb7f81cd82c005354ce5454c3970c507c2045930"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('a50f9ec8-2872-44b4-9036-9d58e5d4c09d'::uuid,'MAXIM GUN','MECHANISM','{}','The machine is a 3,175 kg flying device with a wingspan of 32 m and equipped with two modernized lightweight steam engines of 180 hp (134 kW) each','{}','{}','{"frequency": 1, "text_unit_ids": ["9a992cef03dff7796806f793524bc7e4a0da10b5508fafb928686a95bff271610d193b90ae8a904a7f629cecc08642296f4523195296b24d9e8bcad4e685a7e0"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('9c4f6b13-6950-491e-9de9-53e7328961f4'::uuid,'TEST TRACK','SYSTEM','{}','550 m long rail track built specifically to test the machine''s performance','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["9a992cef03dff7796806f793524bc7e4a0da10b5508fafb928686a95bff271610d193b90ae8a904a7f629cecc08642296f4523195296b24d9e8bcad4e685a7e0", "9a992cef03dff7796806f793524bc7e4a0da10b5508fafb928686a95bff271610d193b90ae8a904a7f629cecc08642296f4523195296b24d9e8bcad4e685a7e0"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('6f2532ca-4d0a-421e-a2cf-5e9663bf71bb'::uuid,'FLIGHT','MECHANISM','{}','Process where the craft travels 180 meters at a speed of 68 km/h before lifting off, hitting an upper rail and crashing','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["9a992cef03dff7796806f793524bc7e4a0da10b5508fafb928686a95bff271610d193b90ae8a904a7f629cecc08642296f4523195296b24d9e8bcad4e685a7e0", "9a992cef03dff7796806f793524bc7e4a0da10b5508fafb928686a95bff271610d193b90ae8a904a7f629cecc08642296f4523195296b24d9e8bcad4e685a7e0"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('dbad2cbf-4eb7-4c0e-867d-8a048f3d0c68'::uuid,'ZHUKOVSKY THEOREM','MODEL','{}','Provides quantitative values for the lift of an aircraft wing and laid foundational theories for aerodynamics through his 1905 lecture and paper','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["9a992cef03dff7796806f793524bc7e4a0da10b5508fafb928686a95bff271610d193b90ae8a904a7f629cecc08642296f4523195296b24d9e8bcad4e685a7e0", "9a992cef03dff7796806f793524bc7e4a0da10b5508fafb928686a95bff271610d193b90ae8a904a7f629cecc08642296f4523195296b24d9e8bcad4e685a7e0"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('5fb106e9-db92-4086-9173-76ef8e3c1b30'::uuid,'AIRWORTHINESS CRITERIA','MECHANISM','{}','Standards for flight safety which led to the tragic crash during early tests due to a lack of control systems','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["9a992cef03dff7796806f793524bc7e4a0da10b5508fafb928686a95bff271610d193b90ae8a904a7f629cecc08642296f4523195296b24d9e8bcad4e685a7e0", "9a992cef03dff7796806f793524bc7e4a0da10b5508fafb928686a95bff271610d193b90ae8a904a7f629cecc08642296f4523195296b24d9e8bcad4e685a7e0"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('6d667dbc-b60d-4d2a-805e-11987ee1c820'::uuid,'ROTATIONAL FORCES','MECHANISM','{}','Forces generated when an object rotates about its longitudinal axis, critical for understanding wing lift—Zhukovsky''s key focus','{}','{}','{"frequency": 1, "text_unit_ids": ["9a992cef03dff7796806f793524bc7e4a0da10b5508fafb928686a95bff271610d193b90ae8a904a7f629cecc08642296f4523195296b24d9e8bcad4e685a7e0"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('f9d0b96a-1847-44fa-95ae-85a917602448'::uuid,'GALAO HUAN FLIGHT','EVENT','{}','(虚构实体，用于引用特定的历史事件——高欢将军放飞风筝的事故)','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["93598286bf41252a5653b865693926a10004c8895f439d179e7df23951875f9be08961897007b5955c71dd93076ae3119f0c8ca810440b7e216291c012b3265d", "93598286bf41252a5653b865693926a10004c8895f439d179e7df23951875f9be08961897007b5955c71dd93076ae3119f0c8ca810440b7e216291c012b3265d"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('d97e92b5-4f0d-4205-a4d6-378a0d94844c'::uuid,'ABBAS IBN FIRNAS''S AIRCRAFT','DEVICE','{}','Developed by Abbas ibn Firnas, this aircraft featured a fabric-covered fuselage and wings, capable of changing altitude and direction – first hang glider in history','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["93598286bf41252a5653b865693926a10004c8895f439d179e7df23951875f9be08961897007b5955c71dd93076ae3119f0c8ca810440b7e216291c012b3265d", "93598286bf41252a5653b865693926a10004c8895f439d179e7df23951875f9be08961897007b5955c71dd93076ae3119f0c8ca810440b7e216291c012b3265d"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('712516fb-8686-4a0a-b673-5453e57d00e0'::uuid,'BAUER''S AERIAL CRAFT','DEVICE','{}','Invented by German inventor Bauer in 1763, this aircraft had a fixed wing and propeller powered by the pilot''s muscle power – considered the first design with these features','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["93598286bf41252a5653b865693926a10004c8895f439d179e7df23951875f9be08961897007b5955c71dd93076ae3119f0c8ca810440b7e216291c012b3265d", "93598286bf41252a5653b865693926a10004c8895f439d179e7df23951875f9be08961897007b5955c71dd93076ae3119f0c8ca810440b7e216291c012b3265d"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics');
