	 ('a1385864-8274-443e-90cb-7065b3dd8a18'::uuid,'ZELEPHINE','DEVICE','{}','Zeppelin refers to airships designed and operated by the Deutsche Zeppelin Reederei company in the early 20th century, including "Hindenburg"','{}','{}','{"frequency": 1, "text_unit_ids": ["3ea69086c604fb251a4059f678ec83b99d67d511efb1c29354f7c0b54808defd6170d2ee03e45660f508dc039db22634dfa65c013414a6a31a8795a58d791441"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('fe84e92a-59a9-492a-a551-93e646d8ac69'::uuid,'LAST PASSENGER ZELLEPHIN','DEVICE','{}','The last passenger Zeppelin, "Hindenburg", was built in 1936 as an example of the evolution in air transportation technology.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 1, "text_unit_ids": ["3ea69086c604fb251a4059f678ec83b99d67d511efb1c29354f7c0b54808defd6170d2ee03e45660f508dc039db22634dfa65c013414a6a31a8795a58d791441"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('fd13cf89-eb68-4ab1-b426-e68257f8e677'::uuid,'FLIGHT SAFETY MECHANISM','MECHANISM','{}','The series of interconnected systems used to ensure safe takeoff and landing, such as those aboard "Hindenburg".','{}','{}','{"frequency": 2, "text_unit_ids": ["3ea69086c604fb251a4059f678ec83b99d67d511efb1c29354f7c0b54808defd6170d2ee03e45660f508dc039db22634dfa65c013414a6a31a8795a58d791441", "3ea69086c604fb251a4059f678ec83b99d67d511efb1c29354f7c0b54808defd6170d2ee03e45660f508dc039db22634dfa65c013414a6a31a8795a58d791441"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
	 ('1726db0b-4400-4ef7-8842-c1299c4d8ad8'::uuid,'ZELEPHINE MATERIALS','MATERIAL','{}','The hull and outer material used on Zeppelins, including "Hindenburg", which was highly flammable, leading to its demise.','{}','{}','{"frequency": 1, "text_unit_ids": ["3ea69086c604fb251a4059f678ec83b99d67d511efb1c29354f7c0b54808defd6170d2ee03e45660f508dc039db22634dfa65c013414a6a31a8795a58d791441"]}','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','2026-07-17 13:19:24.183818','history_development_aeronautics'),
